First report from Ro about the Wassermatrix:
After one day of drinking the oscillated water and occasional test applications on the body with the device, I have the feeling that my body is reformatting itself: All of a sudden I walk very properly, upright and with shoulders back. In the last years I had adopted a hunched-over bad posture due to the complaints and severe pain. I also feel a pleasant warmth inside me - probably because it keeps working. I feel light as a feather - getting up from the chair happens all by itself.
